"title-x-mode\">Title: X Mode</h3><blockquote class=\"kg-blockquote-alt\">\"X with us.\"</blockquote><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-width-full kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2023/01/xmode-smol.gif\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"667\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w600/2023/01/xmode-smol.gif 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1000/2023/01/xmode-smol.gif 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1600/2023/01/xmode-smol.gif 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2023/01/xmode-smol.gif 2000w\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://opensea.io/assets/ethereum/0x8f6ee5787a60959c8daf3d35fa48fd0c49bcca2a/2\">X Mode by MintFace</a></figcaption></figure><p>2023 marks the start of a new chapter.</p><h3 id=\"new-year-new-x\">New Year, New X</h3><blockquote class=\"kg-blockquote-alt\">\"Face it.\"</blockquote><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2023/01/new-year-new-x-smol.gif\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w600/2023/01/new-year-new-x-smol.gif 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1000/2023/01/new-year-new-x-smol.gif 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2023/01/new-year-new-x-smol.gif 1200w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://opensea.io/assets/ethereum/0x8f6ee5787a60959c8daf3d35fa48fd0c49bcca2a/3\">New Year, New X by MintFace</a></figcaption></figure><p></p><p>Back to the grind.</p><h3 id=\"xcoffee\">XCOFFEE</h3><blockquote class=\"kg-blockquote-alt\">\"Neuroglitch.\"</blockquote><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2023/01/XCoffee-smol.gif\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1500\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w600/2023/01/XCoffee-smol.gif 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1000/2023/01/XCoffee-smol.gif 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2023/01/XCoffee-smol.gif 1500w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://opensea.io/assets/ethereum/0x8f6ee5787a60959c8daf3d35fa48fd0c49bcca2a/4\">XCOFFEE by MintFace</a></figcaption></figure><h3 id=\"wen-mint\">WEN MINT</h3><blockquote class=\"kg-blockquote-alt\">\"wen.\"</blockquote><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2023/01/wen-mint.gif\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"2000\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w600/2023/01/wen-mint.gif 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1000/2023/01/wen-mint.gif 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1600/2023/01/wen-mint.gif 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2023/01/wen-mint.gif 2000w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://opensea.io/assets/ethereum/0x8f6ee5787a60959c8daf3d35fa48fd0c49bcca2a/5\">WEN MINT by MintFace</a></figcaption></figure><h3 id=\"xlife-collection\">XLife Collection</h3><p>The XLife collection is my main digital art focus in 2023. XLife will be added to and expanded throughout the year. The edition size will always be 100. The price will always be 0.03 eth. The total number of artworks expected to be released during the year will depend... somewhere between 50 - 100 very approximately.</p><p><strong>On The Line </strong><br />44/100 editions avail.<br />0.03 eth <br /><a href=\"https://app.manifold.xyz/c/on-the-line\">https://app.manifold.xyz/c/on-the-line</a><br /><br /><strong>X Mode</strong><br />51/100 editions avail.<br />0.03 eth <br /><a href=\"https://app.manifold.xyz/c/xmode\">https://app.manifold.xyz/c/xmode</a></p><p><strong>XCOFFEE</strong><br />58/100 editions avail.<br />0.03 eth <br /><a href=\"https://app.manifold.xyz/c/xcoffee\">https://app.manifold.xyz/c/xcoffee</a> </p><p><strong>BONUS: For MintFace readers, one WEN MINT will be airdropped with the purchase of all three artworks (On The Line, X Mode and XCOFFEE). </strong></p><p><strong>DM tx link to @mintfacess on Twitter to redeem.<br /></strong></p><hr />"}